text: Vanessa Lillo Gómez (born 10 March 1983) is a Spanish politician. Since 11 June 2019, she has been a member of the Assembly of Madrid. == References == Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:People from Madrid Category:21st-century Spanish women politicians Category:Members of the 10th Assembly of Madrid
